1
00:00:38,420 --> 00:00:41,060
=How to Train Your Killer=

2
00:00:41,060 --> 00:00:43,900
=Episode 30=

3
00:00:52,350 --> 00:00:53,430
Shiyi?

4
00:00:56,220 --> 00:00:57,320
Didn't I tell you to leave?

5
00:00:57,320 --> 00:00:58,260
Why are you back again?

6
00:00:58,700 --> 00:01:00,470
That day your acting
was overly exaggerated,

7
00:01:00,600 --> 00:01:01,790
and I could tell at a glance

8
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:03,770
that you were deliberately
speaking harshly.

9
00:01:03,800 --> 00:01:05,220
Whose acting was overly exaggerated?

10
00:01:05,220 --> 00:01:06,490
My eyes were swollen from crying.

11
00:01:06,490 --> 00:01:07,310
- Really?
- Mm.

12
00:01:07,760 --> 00:01:08,600
I didn't see it.

13
00:01:09,710 --> 00:01:10,550
But...

14
00:01:12,120 --> 00:01:12,960
I could feel it.

15
00:01:13,680 --> 00:01:15,350
Even though we've switched back,

16
00:01:15,760 --> 00:01:17,640
I still seem to sense your thoughts.

17
00:01:18,120 --> 00:01:19,590
If Yuan Chen hadn't reminded me,

18
00:01:20,070 --> 00:01:21,430
I'd think it was my own problem.

19
00:01:23,870 --> 00:01:24,710
It's not like that.

20
00:01:26,760 --> 00:01:28,310
Hey, Shiyi.

21
00:01:32,100 --> 00:01:33,590
Before, no matter how upset you were,

22
00:01:33,590 --> 00:01:34,790
you always kept it to yourself.

23
00:01:35,560 --> 00:01:37,510
Why are you crying so easily now?

24
00:01:39,700 --> 00:01:41,350
I don't know what's wrong
with me either.

25
00:01:42,230 --> 00:01:43,070
I just…

26
00:01:44,640 --> 00:01:47,040
I just can't hold it in.

27
00:01:48,280 --> 00:01:49,950
I keep wanting to cry.

28
00:01:52,350 --> 00:01:53,560
Could it be

29
00:01:53,870 --> 00:01:55,760
that even though you've swapped bodies,

30
00:01:56,150 --> 00:01:57,790
you can still empathize with each other?

31
00:02:01,870 --> 00:02:02,870
Is that so?

32
00:02:03,430 --> 00:02:04,270
That's right.

33
00:02:04,870 --> 00:02:05,950
Think about it.

34
00:02:06,400 --> 00:02:07,240
Shiyi,

35
00:02:07,400 --> 00:02:08,750
you used to be so carefree.

36
00:02:09,240 --> 00:02:11,470
Look at yourself now.

37
00:02:12,800 --> 00:02:13,750
So,

38
00:02:14,590 --> 00:02:17,560
she must've felt even sadder
than I did that day.

39
00:02:17,910 --> 00:02:18,870
That's what I meant.

40
00:02:19,630 --> 00:02:20,630
That young lady

41
00:02:21,000 --> 00:02:23,080
said those harsh words
to drive you away on purpose.

42
00:02:25,560 --> 00:02:26,520
Now.

43
00:02:27,000 --> 00:02:27,870
Right now.

44
00:02:27,870 --> 00:02:29,280
Take the Spike with you

45
00:02:29,680 --> 00:02:31,240
to bring that young lady back to me.

46
00:02:31,630 --> 00:02:32,470
Don't be afraid.

47
00:02:34,630 --> 00:02:36,080
I'll take care of your remains.

48
00:02:42,150 --> 00:02:42,990
Yuan Chen,

49
00:02:44,030 --> 00:02:44,870
I must admit,

50
00:02:47,370 --> 00:02:48,680
you do know how to comfort people.

51
00:02:49,310 --> 00:02:50,150
Of course.

52
00:02:57,240 --> 00:02:58,750
I have nothing to hide.

53
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:00,680
Why would I waste time
on tender feelings?

54
00:03:02,400 --> 00:03:03,240
Really?

55
00:03:04,590 --> 00:03:06,190
I still remember that day someone said,

56
00:03:06,400 --> 00:03:08,030
"Your Highness, I will take my leave."

57
00:03:08,240 --> 00:03:09,400
That leave lasted a lifetime.

58
00:03:10,150 --> 00:03:11,360
That's truly hilarious.

59
00:03:11,360 --> 00:03:12,610
Is that so? I don't recall.

60
00:03:12,610 --> 00:03:13,590
Anyway, I didn't say it.

61
00:03:13,590 --> 00:03:15,120
You don't remember? It was cheesy.

62
00:03:15,120 --> 00:03:16,030
Still don't remember?

63
00:03:16,030 --> 00:03:16,870
Enough!

64
00:03:17,470 --> 00:03:19,030
Stop flirting over there.

65
00:03:19,240 --> 00:03:20,280
Perfect timing.

66
00:03:21,120 --> 00:03:22,750
I shall deal with you all at once,

67
00:03:23,190 --> 00:03:24,470
and get it off my mind.

68
00:03:25,870 --> 00:03:26,710
It seems

69
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:29,710
you truly do fear me.

70
00:03:31,680 --> 00:03:32,750
What a joke.

71
00:03:33,470 --> 00:03:35,470
I rule a nation now.

72
00:03:35,470 --> 00:03:36,560
Would I fear you?

73
00:03:38,030 --> 00:03:39,310
A ruler of the realm?

74
00:03:39,680 --> 00:03:41,030
You freak,

75
00:03:41,240 --> 00:03:42,240
ignoring your own body

76
00:03:42,240 --> 00:03:43,960
while obsessing over someone else's.

77
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:45,150
Maybe one day

78
00:03:45,310 --> 00:03:46,840
you will forget who you even are.

79
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:49,840
You reckless fool!

80
00:03:51,130 --> 00:03:52,430
This monster is now more powerful

81
00:03:52,430 --> 00:03:53,960
than Lingyi and Lingsan combined.

82
00:03:54,400 --> 00:03:55,240
Can you handle it?

83
00:03:55,870 --> 00:03:57,190
A man must never admit he can't.

84
00:03:57,520 --> 00:03:58,360
Do you forget?

85
00:03:58,910 --> 00:04:00,310
Don't be too sure of yourself.

86
00:04:00,680 --> 00:04:01,910
Hold on a moment.

87
00:04:02,400 --> 00:04:03,470
I still have a trump card,

88
00:04:04,080 --> 00:04:05,750
specially to deal with you

89
00:04:05,910 --> 00:04:07,120
from beyond the frontier.

90
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:18,070
That's impressive.

91
00:04:32,040 --> 00:04:33,680
So this is the trump card you spoke of?

92
00:04:36,800 --> 00:04:37,640
Shiyi,

93
00:04:37,870 --> 00:04:40,920
you once said my swordsmanship
is too rigid, easy to break.

94
00:04:41,210 --> 00:04:42,670
But using strength to overpower skill

95
00:04:42,870 --> 00:04:44,120
is the essence of my sword path.

96
00:04:49,430 --> 00:04:50,600
Do you dare to kill me?

97
00:04:50,900 --> 00:04:52,660
Remember, this body belongs
to the emperor.

98
00:04:55,620 --> 00:04:56,510
You…

99
00:04:56,510 --> 00:04:57,600
You what?

100
00:04:57,950 --> 00:04:59,430
I've long grown tired of you.

101
00:05:03,560 --> 00:05:04,430
How was that?

102
00:05:04,430 --> 00:05:06,160
Pretty swift move this time, huh?

103
00:05:07,270 --> 00:05:08,270
Not bad, I'd say.

104
00:05:09,270 --> 00:05:10,430
You did hesitate though.

105
00:05:10,500 --> 00:05:11,660
Still, you've grown stronger.

106
00:05:12,640 --> 00:05:13,480
I comprehended

107
00:05:13,480 --> 00:05:15,190
this swordsmanship from Bai Jun.

108
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:16,440
Impressive, right?

109
00:05:17,070 --> 00:05:17,920
Not bad.

110
00:05:19,040 --> 00:05:19,880
Alright then.

111
00:05:20,480 --> 00:05:21,390
What do we do with him?

112
00:05:23,390 --> 00:05:25,190
I'm just worried that once he wakes up,

113
00:05:25,190 --> 00:05:26,360
Ling Yu will come after you.

114
00:05:28,000 --> 00:05:29,040
Well, we can't exactly

115
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:31,160
let Wu Yun stay in his body forever.

116
00:05:33,870 --> 00:05:35,000
Then you decide.

117
00:05:36,120 --> 00:05:36,960
Alright.

118
00:06:05,270 --> 00:06:06,360
Someone!

119
00:06:09,630 --> 00:06:10,470
Some...

120
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:18,270
Wait, how did I end up as Eunuch Leng?

121
00:06:20,160 --> 00:06:21,720
Someone!

122
00:06:30,040 --> 00:06:31,360
It's gone.

123
00:06:32,560 --> 00:06:34,600
It's really gone!

124
00:06:36,920 --> 00:06:40,510
Someone! Help!

125
00:06:41,950 --> 00:06:42,800
Your Majesty,

126
00:06:42,950 --> 00:06:44,000
we've come to rescue you.

127
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:47,400
Qingyao,

128
00:06:47,630 --> 00:06:49,480
what happened?

129
00:06:51,240 --> 00:06:52,160
Your Majesty,

130
00:06:52,480 --> 00:06:55,240
this matter is quite strange.

131
00:06:56,120 --> 00:06:57,870
But you must trust me.

132
00:07:01,000 --> 00:07:02,240
So,

133
00:07:02,560 --> 00:07:06,360
can I ever change back?

134
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:16,400
Perhaps this might make it possible.

135
00:07:20,600 --> 00:07:21,600
Hero Shi,

136
00:07:22,510 --> 00:07:23,750
I'll leave it to you then.

137
00:07:24,600 --> 00:07:25,830
You can count on me.

138
00:07:26,600 --> 00:07:27,560
However,

139
00:07:27,700 --> 00:07:29,410
you have to trade it
with your belongings.

140
00:07:31,190 --> 00:07:32,310
What do you want?

141
00:07:36,510 --> 00:07:38,630
The person second only
to the country in your heart.

142
00:07:49,360 --> 00:07:51,040
Do you think this will help?

143
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:53,480
I'm not sure either.

144
00:07:54,270 --> 00:07:56,360
What if he will refuse to admit it

145
00:07:56,920 --> 00:07:58,190
after he changes back later?

146
00:08:01,500 --> 00:08:02,950
Then I'll just have to take you away.

147
00:08:39,630 --> 00:08:40,720
It's really changed back.

148
00:08:43,360 --> 00:08:44,550
It truly has changed back.

149
00:08:47,870 --> 00:08:48,720
Tell me,

150
00:08:49,440 --> 00:08:51,320
are you truly Ling Yu?

151
00:08:52,170 --> 00:08:53,150
What do you mean by that?

152
00:08:53,390 --> 00:08:54,960
I need some kind of proof.

153
00:08:55,390 --> 00:08:56,240
What proof?

154
00:08:57,030 --> 00:08:58,360
That night, I tried to kill you.

155
00:08:59,390 --> 00:09:00,390
And I kicked you once.

156
00:09:00,550 --> 00:09:02,030
Was it with my left foot or right?

157
00:09:03,320 --> 00:09:04,160
This…

158
00:09:05,600 --> 00:09:06,480
How would I know?

159
00:09:07,150 --> 00:09:08,200
You definitely know.

160
00:09:09,200 --> 00:09:10,550
Because you found it humiliating.

161
00:09:11,270 --> 00:09:12,240
Every night,

162
00:09:12,500 --> 00:09:14,100
you might still wake up
from bad dreams.

163
00:09:15,150 --> 00:09:16,200
Hero Shi,

164
00:09:16,260 --> 00:09:17,320
don't push things too far.

165
00:09:17,320 --> 00:09:18,160
Speak.

166
00:09:18,790 --> 00:09:19,630
Your Majesty,

167
00:09:21,390 --> 00:09:22,360
I advise you

168
00:09:22,720 --> 00:09:23,960
to say it now.

169
00:09:24,600 --> 00:09:26,790
After all, this matter concerns

170
00:09:27,100 --> 00:09:28,610
whether you are truly yourself or not.

171
00:09:32,080 --> 00:09:33,390
Hero Shi, you...

172
00:09:34,270 --> 00:09:35,630
You kicked with your left foot.

173
00:09:36,360 --> 00:09:38,320
When I fell, I also bumped my butt,

174
00:09:39,620 --> 00:09:40,790
and it hurt for several days.

175
00:09:43,240 --> 00:09:45,000
My apologies, Your Majesty.

176
00:09:45,200 --> 00:09:46,660
Now that you've returned to yourself,

177
00:09:47,960 --> 00:09:49,790
you should honor the promise between us.

178
00:09:52,480 --> 00:09:54,120
Shiyi, I'm craving a steamed bun.

179
00:09:55,120 --> 00:09:56,200
I'll buy you one in a bit.

180
00:09:58,150 --> 00:09:59,150
I'll buy you one later.

181
00:10:01,390 --> 00:10:02,270
Hey, watch your step.

182
00:10:04,200 --> 00:10:05,110
What else do you need?

183
00:10:05,870 --> 00:10:06,840
These flowers look good.

184
00:10:08,770 --> 00:10:09,960
These flowers look quite nice.

185
00:10:10,670 --> 00:10:12,480
Let Yuan Chen buy you two bottles later.

186
00:10:12,720 --> 00:10:14,480
- Let Yuan Chen buy?
- Yeah.

187
00:10:14,480 --> 00:10:15,390
What are you thinking?

188
00:10:15,480 --> 00:10:16,510
All our money's with him.

189
00:10:16,510 --> 00:10:17,480
Yuan Chen!

190
00:10:24,550 --> 00:10:26,000
He's dozing off again, of course.

191
00:10:27,870 --> 00:10:29,150
You two again?

192
00:10:30,270 --> 00:10:31,450
Yuan Chen,

193
00:10:31,450 --> 00:10:32,510
why do you always look like

194
00:10:32,510 --> 00:10:33,720
you just woke up?

195
00:10:34,360 --> 00:10:35,820
(Moyu Pavilion)
Come on.

196
00:10:35,840 --> 00:10:37,870
It's all your fault
for disturbing my sweet dreams

197
00:10:37,870 --> 00:10:39,270
early in the morning every time.

198
00:10:40,840 --> 00:10:41,840
Hey, Shiyi.

199
00:10:42,550 --> 00:10:44,000
The fact that you came back alive

200
00:10:45,390 --> 00:10:47,270
truly surprises me.

201
00:10:47,840 --> 00:10:49,200
If he doesn't come back,

202
00:10:49,630 --> 00:10:51,960
you'll keep those jewels for yourself,
won't you?

203
00:10:52,600 --> 00:10:53,670
Hey, what do you mean?

204
00:10:53,960 --> 00:10:54,840
Shiyi,

205
00:10:54,840 --> 00:10:56,750
why does she paint me as so scheming?

206
00:10:57,000 --> 00:10:58,320
What do you think?

207
00:10:59,080 --> 00:10:59,920
Hand it over.

208
00:11:00,630 --> 00:11:01,480
Hand it over.

209
00:11:01,480 --> 00:11:02,320
Come on.

210
00:11:02,960 --> 00:11:06,270
I can't quite recall where I put it.

211
00:11:07,240 --> 00:11:08,630
- Hurry.
- Go find it.

212
00:11:10,100 --> 00:11:11,440
- Where is it?
- Keep your eyes on him.

213
00:11:11,440 --> 00:11:12,230
Move.

214
00:11:17,000 --> 00:11:17,870
After all,

215
00:11:17,870 --> 00:11:18,960
I lent you a great hand.

216
00:11:19,050 --> 00:11:20,550
How come no one thinks of repaying me?

217
00:11:20,870 --> 00:11:22,000
Haven't you taken

218
00:11:22,000 --> 00:11:23,320
enough advantage of me already?

219
00:11:23,320 --> 00:11:24,160
Exactly.

220
00:11:24,440 --> 00:11:25,280
So petty!

221
00:11:25,670 --> 00:11:27,360
How did you two become so petty?

222
00:11:27,870 --> 00:11:29,000
We have no choice.

223
00:11:29,150 --> 00:11:30,050
In the martial world,

224
00:11:30,050 --> 00:11:31,460
we've got to keep some silver on us.

225
00:11:31,460 --> 00:11:32,270
- Right?
- Silver...

226
00:11:32,270 --> 00:11:33,110
You get what I mean.

227
00:11:33,180 --> 00:11:34,030
Come on.

228
00:11:34,030 --> 00:11:34,870
Here.

229
00:11:42,840 --> 00:11:44,200
What? Give it to me.

230
00:11:44,200 --> 00:11:45,580
Didn't you already return it to me?

231
00:11:45,580 --> 00:11:46,870
Who return it to you?

232
00:11:46,870 --> 00:11:47,720
You did.

233
00:11:47,720 --> 00:11:48,670
It's been ages.

234
00:11:48,670 --> 00:11:49,550
Are you still mad?

235
00:11:50,480 --> 00:11:51,550
Fine, take it.

236
00:11:51,550 --> 00:11:52,390
Mm.

237
00:11:52,700 --> 00:11:54,080
Don't expect me to return it later.

238
00:11:54,080 --> 00:11:54,870
Alright.

239
00:11:58,030 --> 00:11:59,390
Look at how nervous you are.

240
00:11:59,390 --> 00:12:01,000
After all,

241
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:02,240
I almost became an empress once.

242
00:12:02,240 --> 00:12:03,600
Do you think I'd be short of money?

243
00:12:04,240 --> 00:12:05,720
I knew it.

244
00:12:07,200 --> 00:12:08,480
But that vile em...

245
00:12:09,300 --> 00:12:11,650
Why would that vile emperor
let the two of you go so easily?

246
00:12:16,260 --> 00:12:17,150
Let's go.

247
00:12:17,160 --> 00:12:18,010
Mm.

248
00:12:18,510 --> 00:12:19,350
Wait.

249
00:12:22,240 --> 00:12:24,440
Your Majesty, are you going back
on your word?

250
00:12:25,440 --> 00:12:26,480
If I can change you back,

251
00:12:26,900 --> 00:12:28,320
I can naturally turn you back again.

252
00:12:29,120 --> 00:12:30,550
Back then, you asked me,

253
00:12:31,750 --> 00:12:32,910
which weighed more,

254
00:12:33,910 --> 00:12:35,000
the realm or Qingyao.

255
00:12:37,030 --> 00:12:38,480
At that time, I chose the realm.

256
00:12:40,480 --> 00:12:42,080
But if I were to choose again today,

257
00:12:44,600 --> 00:12:46,670
I would only wish to stay
by Qingyao's side.

258
00:12:49,270 --> 00:12:50,440
You would make that choice,

259
00:12:51,270 --> 00:12:52,200
because

260
00:12:52,960 --> 00:12:54,480
you already possess the realm.

261
00:12:59,510 --> 00:13:00,750
But I believe

262
00:13:02,360 --> 00:13:03,200
that you

263
00:13:04,360 --> 00:13:05,910
will surely become a wise ruler.

264
00:13:20,300 --> 00:13:22,240
An assassin struck
the Crown Prince's Residence.

265
00:13:24,120 --> 00:13:26,200
Empress Gu was killed in the chaos.

266
00:13:28,000 --> 00:13:29,360
From this day on,

267
00:13:31,200 --> 00:13:33,240
Gu Qingyao will vanish from this world.

268
00:13:40,360 --> 00:13:41,480
Go now, quickly.

269
00:13:45,080 --> 00:13:45,920
Let's go.

270
00:13:58,320 --> 00:14:00,630
What will you do after this?

271
00:14:02,240 --> 00:14:03,080
No plans at all.

272
00:14:03,080 --> 00:14:04,360
- Go wherever we wish.
- Right.

273
00:14:04,360 --> 00:14:05,960
Maybe Jiangnan,

274
00:14:06,100 --> 00:14:07,840
or beyond the frontier,
or the Northern Sea.

275
00:14:07,840 --> 00:14:08,810
As long as I'm with you,

276
00:14:08,810 --> 00:14:09,890
anywhere under the vast sky

277
00:14:09,890 --> 00:14:10,870
is a good place to be.

278
00:14:13,790 --> 00:14:14,630
Then,

279
00:14:15,320 --> 00:14:16,440
let's start with Jiangnan.

280
00:14:17,390 --> 00:14:18,790
I don't want to know the reason.

281
00:14:18,790 --> 00:14:19,890
If you say so, then just go.

282
00:14:25,530 --> 00:14:26,840
We're off. No need to see us off.

283
00:14:27,080 --> 00:14:28,910
This time, you're truly leaving?

284
00:14:31,440 --> 00:14:32,280
I'm going.

285
00:14:33,390 --> 00:14:34,230
Take care.

286
00:14:35,360 --> 00:14:36,440
Stop dawdling.

287
00:14:37,030 --> 00:14:37,870
Take care.

288
00:14:38,630 --> 00:14:39,470
Go now.

289
00:14:41,790 --> 00:14:42,630
Farewell.

290
00:14:42,910 --> 00:14:43,750
Let's go.

291
00:14:46,870 --> 00:14:47,710
Much appreciated.

292
00:14:56,630 --> 00:14:58,360
Didn't you say you'd give me flowers?

293
00:14:59,800 --> 00:15:01,690
There are plenty of wildflowers
along the road.

294
00:15:01,800 --> 00:15:02,970
I'll pick some for you later.

295
00:15:03,720 --> 00:15:04,720
And the steamed buns?

296
00:15:05,150 --> 00:15:06,000
Steamed buns?

297
00:15:06,000 --> 00:15:06,840
I'll make it for you.

298
00:15:07,440 --> 00:15:08,280
Alright.

299
00:15:10,960 --> 00:15:12,480
You seem to be in good spirits.

300
00:15:12,790 --> 00:15:13,630
Of course I am.

301
00:15:15,270 --> 00:15:16,200
How's it going?

302
00:15:16,200 --> 00:15:18,000
You're about to roam the world with me.

303
00:15:18,670 --> 00:15:19,510
Any regrets?

304
00:15:20,440 --> 00:15:22,240
Of course I do.

305
00:15:23,700 --> 00:15:24,890
I regret not having spent days

306
00:15:24,890 --> 00:15:26,600
like this with you earlier.

307
00:15:36,360 --> 00:15:37,200
What's wrong?

308
00:15:39,790 --> 00:15:40,840
Why do I feel like

309
00:15:40,840 --> 00:15:42,150
that person looks a bit familiar?

310
00:15:42,550 --> 00:15:44,000
Do you still remember

311
00:15:44,200 --> 00:15:46,390
that we dealt with before,

312
00:15:47,030 --> 00:15:47,870
that freak,

313
00:15:47,870 --> 00:15:49,260
the freak from beyond the frontier,

314
00:15:49,260 --> 00:15:49,990
what was his name?

315
00:15:50,720 --> 00:15:52,480
Wu… Wu…

316
00:15:52,820 --> 00:15:54,500
(Mullet roe)
Mullet roe.

317
00:15:56,360 --> 00:15:58,360
I think his name is Wu Yun.

318
00:15:59,270 --> 00:16:00,110
Forget it.

319
00:16:00,240 --> 00:16:01,630
Sometimes I wonder,

320
00:16:01,870 --> 00:16:03,670
do you think Ling Yu
ever got changed back?

321
00:16:07,360 --> 00:16:08,480
I am teasing you.

322
00:16:08,480 --> 00:16:09,440
You actually believe me.

323
00:16:10,240 --> 00:16:11,240
Silly one.

324
00:16:18,910 --> 00:16:20,080
There are so many people.

325
00:16:20,080 --> 00:16:20,920
What's there to fear?

326
00:16:53,440 --> 00:16:54,280
Let's go.

327
00:16:58,000 --> 00:16:59,080
Come on, hurry.

328
00:17:54,510 --> 00:17:57,110
♪When a breeze passes by♪

329
00:17:57,630 --> 00:18:00,950
♪The sand and wind burn with longing♪

330
00:18:00,950 --> 00:18:03,590
♪Fearless even when thirst
goes unquenched♪

331
00:18:03,910 --> 00:18:07,070
♪Like a camel wandering
with eyes closed♪

332
00:18:07,430 --> 00:18:10,390
♪When the rain quietly settles♪

333
00:18:10,390 --> 00:18:13,710
♪I think of our sorrow yet unknown♪

334
00:18:13,910 --> 00:18:16,630
♪No need to hum the song of the wind♪

335
00:18:16,790 --> 00:18:20,430
♪Ignoring the sky darkening before us♪

336
00:18:20,590 --> 00:18:22,190
♪I finally understood that truth♪

337
00:18:22,190 --> 00:18:23,670
♪Yet you have already faded away♪

338
00:18:23,870 --> 00:18:25,510
♪I lose my way in the night♪

339
00:18:25,510 --> 00:18:26,990
♪Not knowing how to still my heart♪

340
00:18:26,990 --> 00:18:28,670
♪Loving you feels like lifetimes apart♪

341
00:18:28,670 --> 00:18:31,630
♪Yet longing flows back into verse♪

342
00:18:32,070 --> 00:18:34,510
♪For you and me to meet again♪

343
00:18:34,950 --> 00:18:37,790
♪We must cross a thousand years
of promises♪

344
00:18:38,070 --> 00:18:40,150
♪In the pouring rain♪

345
00:18:40,150 --> 00:18:44,510
♪As if you are still by my side♪
